Welsh (12/19/2020)
Wedi - Castle 2 
Streak: 466 Days 
Mae Megan wedi mynd i'r parti. (Megan has gone to the party.)
Mae Morgan wedi mynd i'r gwaith yn gynnar heddiw. (Morgan has gone to work early today)
Dych chi wedi mynd i'r gwaith eto. (Have you gone to work yet?) 
Dw i eisiau mynd i'r ysgol yn gynnar. (I want to go to the school early)
Dych chi wedi mynd i'r parc?  (Have you gone to the park?)
Dych chi wedi mynd i'r swyddfa eto? (Have you gone to the office yet?)
Dw i eisiau mynd i'r ysgol. (I want to go to school.)
Ydy hi wedi cerdded i'r swyddfa.  (Has she walked to the office?)
Dych chi wedi mynd i'r parc. (Have you gone to the park?)
Ydw.  Dw i wedi mynd i'r parti.  Yes.  I have gone to the party.
